12:00.900 --> 12:02.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

12:02.366 --> 12:05.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ROY BLUNT: Well, it's pretty
late to come up with a new plan.

12:05.533 --> 12:09.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
