legislatively what you
want to be talking about.

12:09.566 --> 12:12.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
You want to be talking
about what you're
focused on at the time.

12:12.533 --> 12:17.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think it's fair to say that
it's hard to get 50 senators
out of 52 to vote for a package

12:20.733 --> 12:22.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
this complicated.

12:22.800 --> 12:26.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Actually, Judy, the more that
members know about this, in
many ways, the harder it is

12:28.833 --> 12:31.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to make that final decision,
