12:42.433 --> 12:43.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

12:43.933 --> 12:47.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ROY BLUNT: Well, I think we have
had a three-step plan in mind.

12:47.066 --> 12:52.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We pass this bill that did as
