clear the way for Democrats and

12:55.066 --> 12:57.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Republicans to work
together later.

12:57.933 --> 13:02.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The secretary of health and
human services would look at
the 1,400-plus rules that the

13:04.900 --> 13:08.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
