ability to define and see how
those could be better defined,

13:08.400 --> 13:13.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
so they were better for
families, better for
access and then, when
that's done, get down

13:15.433 --> 13:20.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
