13:30.633 --> 13:32.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Where
you do finally work with
Democrats, Democrats and
Republicans together?

13:32.533 --> 13:33.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

13:33.533 --> 13:34.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ROY BLUNT: Right.

13:34.533 --> 13:35.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Last thing...

13:35.533 --> 13:36.700 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

13:36.700 --> 13:38.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ROY BLUNT: And that's
going to happen.

13:38.833 --> 13:40.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That has to happen to expand
the way more people can get
more insurance in groups, to

13:40.300 --> 13:43.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
look at things like more
transparency from providers.

13:43.433 --> 13:45.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
That eventually has to happen.

13:45.466 --> 13:49.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But it doesn't have to
happen to stabilize the
