over 40 percent of the counties.

14:04.966 --> 14:08.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if you only have would
be choice, you really
don't have any choice.

14:08.233 --> 14:13.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You either buy that policy or
pay the penalty, and all those
things will happen if we don't

14:13.966 --> 14:16.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
change the current law.

14:16.033 --> 14:18.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Last thing I want
to ask you about, Senator Blunt,
and that is the president's

14:18.166 --> 14:20.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
