14:30.700 --> 14:31.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What's your reaction?

14:31.833 --> 14:33.866 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

14:33.866 --> 14:37.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROY BLUNT: Well, there's no
doubt that cable news hosts can
say things that the president

14:37.533 --> 14:40.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
