President (through translator):
The North Korean nuclear issue

21:08.333 --> 21:10.500 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
must be resolved, without fail.

21:10.500 --> 21:15.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I also urge Pyongyang
to promptly return to
the negotiating table
for denuclearization

21:16.000 --> 21:18.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of the Korean Peninsula.

21:18.500 --> 21:21.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump and I
will employ both sanctions
and dialogue in a
phased and comprehensive

21:21.366 --> 21:23.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
approach.

21:23.433 --> 21:26.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And based on this, we both
pledged to seek a fundamental
resolution of the North Korean

21:26.133 --> 21:28.133 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
nuclear problem.

21:28.133 --> 21:31.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
