at Georgetown University
and chair of the U.S.
Korea Institute at Johns

22:37.266 --> 22:38.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Hopkins University.

22:38.500 --> 22:40.000 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Welcome to the "NewsHour."

22:40.000 --> 22:42.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ROBERT GALLUCCI, Georgetown
University: Thanks very much.

22:42.100 --> 22:44.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Do you think
