22:44.233 --> 22:46.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
plan for how to deal
with North Korea?

22:46.233 --> 22:51.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROBERT GALLUCCI: I think today's
meeting is a success, in the
sense that the United States

22:53.133 --> 22:56.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
end and the South Koreans
