strength of that alliance
are those military exercises.

26:41.233 --> 26:44.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So that will be not high on
our agenda to give up easily.

26:44.266 --> 26:48.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Is that something that might
be on the table, along with
the nuclear weapons program of

26:48.566 --> 26:50.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the North Koreans?

26:50.000 --> 26:51.233 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Plausibly.

26:51.233 --> 26:52.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But that's pretty
much down the road.

26:52.533 --> 26:55.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I wouldn't imagine
negotiations would begin there.

26:55.666 --> 26:59.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They would begin with
talks about talks, I think,
without preconditions.

26:59.333 --> 27:01.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Last night.

27:01.566 --> 27:03.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Do you think the Trump
administration has any
interest in any of the
things you're taking

27:03.766 --> 27:05.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
about?

27:05.566 --> 27:08.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROBERT GALLUCCI: I don't
know what the Trump
administration is interested in.

27:08.466 --> 27:13.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There have been mentions by the
secretary of state, secretary
of defense and even the

27:14.833 --> 27:17.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
president of possibly talking
with the North Koreans.

27:17.066 --> 27:22.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I worry that, in their minds,
are preconditions that will make
negotiations someplace between

27:22.966 --> 27:24.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
