27:24.933 --> 27:27.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Robert
Gallucci, Georgetown University,
thank you very much for being

27:27.733 --> 27:29.033 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

27:29.033 --> 27:34.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ROBERT GALLUCCI:
Thank you very much.

