28:42.833 --> 28:47.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
By day, Rivera is
police, by night, a young
professional boxer.

28:49.433 --> 28:51.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
But he says, as a
boy, his mother didn't
let him play outside.

28:51.633 --> 28:55.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
VIDAL RIVERA: It was
just too dangerous.

28:55.100 --> 28:57.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
There was just
too much going on.

28:57.200 --> 29:02.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She feared that something could
happen, someone high, driving
a car, a shoot-out, everything.

29:04.566 --> 29:09.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Rivera is part
