29:31.833 --> 29:33.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It was the fear that you had.

29:33.933 --> 29:38.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Historically,
one of the country's most
impoverished and violent cities,

29:38.633 --> 29:43.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
