people, nearly all of them
Latino and African-American.

29:45.533 --> 29:48.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And a number of the department's
newer officers have been
recruited from the community.

29:50.666 --> 29:54.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Police Chief Scott Thomson
also grew up in Camden, and he
has been largely responsible

29:54.533 --> 29:56.000 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
