doubts, opposition to the
bill as proposed last Friday.

41:52.266 --> 41:54.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And what happened?

41:54.333 --> 41:57.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Joining the state's governor,
who pointed out that the
rate of uninsured children in

41:59.766 --> 42:03.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
