a National Enquirer
investigation into their

46:21.566 --> 46:23.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
relationship will be spiked.

46:23.566 --> 46:27.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that's sort of mafioso,
extortion behavior.

46:27.333 --> 46:28.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That's beyond normal
White House behavior.

46:28.966 --> 46:31.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's beyond political hardball.

46:31.333 --> 46:36.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's sort of using your media
allies, The National Enquirer
and the Trump administration,

46:37.066 --> 46:39.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to take down enemies.

46:39.166 --> 46:42.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's not something we
have seen in America since
maybe Nixon, or maybe never.

46:42.766 --> 46:47.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's true,
Mark, we haven't seen
anything like this in a while.

46:47.233 --> 46:49.400 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: We haven't.

46:49.400 --> 46:52.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But I think David's
point about extortion
certainly strengthens
the position of James

46:52.466 --> 46:57.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Comey, that threats
and extortion or a hint
of extortion is part
of the modus operandi.

47:00.466 --> 47:02.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
To Republicans...

47:02.100 --> 47:03.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I mean,
we should say the White
House is denying it.

47:03.300 --> 47:05.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: The White
