publications of our time.

47:24.133 --> 47:28.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But, Judy, I remember
when Republicans used
to get upset and angry
at Bill Clinton because

47:28.200 --> 47:31.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
