tie in the Oval Office.

47:31.866 --> 47:36.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Donald Trump, who
is supposed to be this
great deal-maker, I mean,
Joe and Mika Brzezinski

47:36.533 --> 47:41.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
