audience, and probably 1
percent of the people.

47:46.000 --> 47:50.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And he just made them a
national -- everybody now
knows about this show.

47:50.866 --> 47:53.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
