chance of things going right.

51:51.366 --> 51:56.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Perhaps my daughter's story
might one day be counted in a
future study, and her success

51:56.033 --> 52:01.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
will serve as a tick
against those frightening,
bigger numbers, because
there is an alternate

52:02.633 --> 52:06.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
ending that includes
the full picture, and
it can be beautiful.

